HEALTH CARE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; WELFARE PROGRAMS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; USER 
FEES; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- TAXES; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- BUDGET 
</P>
