CONTRIBUTIONS; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS -- FINANCES; CALIFORNIA FAIR 
POLITICAL PRACTICES COMMISSION; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; LOS 
ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES; CONFLICT OF INTEREST; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; 
