<TEXT>
<P>
Many county shoppers can buy gifts and mail them to their out-of-town relatives 
without leaving the shopping mall. The U.S. Postal Service has set up booths in 
selected malls throughout the county. The booths offer the services found in 
any post office, such as parcel post and express, priority, insured and 
registered mails. Products available include holiday stamps, padded envelopes 
and shipping cartons. The booths will open Friday and continue to operate 
through Dec. 23, except as noted. 
