<TEXT>
<P>
Save Our Bastanchury -- A report on Nov. 9 that the Save Our Bastanchury group 
in Fullerton had sued the city over a ballot measure was incorrect. In fact, 
the City Council has voted to sue the group over the wording of the ballot 
measure, which would let voters decide whether Bastanchury Road should be 
widened. 
</P>
